message: Only 10 days left until TREK 2015!!! If you are still thinking about coming to TREK, what are you waiting for?! Join us for 5 days of worship, community, training, and outdoor activities (among other wonderful things)! Registration is open until May 11. The cost is $349 for freshmen and $369 for upperclassmen. If you register by tomorrow you can still get $25 off, and the next 6 people to register and pay the $39 deposit will get an additional $50 off. You can find more information and register at http://www.uppermidwest.org/summer-missions/trek/
